{"type":null,"faqId":11992,"title":"G620-L72  通话时手机离开耳部后仍然为黑屏，如何解决？","answer":"<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">手机屏幕上方靠近听筒的位置内置有接近光传感器。</span> \n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在通话过程中，手机贴近耳部或有其他物体遮挡住上方的屏幕时，手机会自动关闭屏幕，离开遮挡物后屏幕会自动点亮方便您操作。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若在通话过程中，手机离开耳部仍然为黑屏，请检查上方的屏幕是否被遮挡。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">为了保证您的正常使用，请注意不要用手机套或其他物体遮挡听筒及其附近的屏幕。使用屏幕保护膜时，也请勿遮盖感应器部位，建议您购买本手机专用屏幕保护膜。</span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":137,"faqType":"通话与联系人","useful":0,"unUseful":6,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2798","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Calls-contacts","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1398825173000,"seriesProductName":"G620-L72","visitedTimes":211,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"通话时手机离开耳部后仍然为黑屏","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}